Package: raybevel
Type: Package
Title: Generates Polygon Straight Skeletons and 3D Bevels
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tyler Morgan-Wall
Maintainer: Tyler Morgan-Wall <tylermw@gmail.com>
Description: Generates polygon straight skeletons using the `CGAL` library. Provides functions to create and visualize interior polygon offsets, 3D beveled polygons, and 3D roof models.
